title: Rumor Roundup: Brock Lesnar match, SummerSlam, Money in the Bank, more!
content: Speculating on the rumors surrounding pro wrestling is a favored pastime of many fans, perhaps second only to actually watching the matches. In this daily column, we take a look at the latest rumors being churned out by the pro wrestling rumor mill. Important reminder: Rumors are just that -- rumors. None of this has been confirmed as legitimate news or fact, its just circulating around the pro wrestling rumor mill. We track rumor accuracy in a weekly feature called Rumor Look Back you can find here. Remember, take it all with a grain of salt. Rumors for the Day: The Observer says the plan as of now is for Brock Lesnar’s next title defense to headline SummerSlam in August. It’s not clear yet
